net.hudup.core.alg

Interface DuplicatableAlg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Alg, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Neighbor2dCF, NeighborItemBasedCF, NeighborUserBasedCF

    public interface DuplicatableAlg
extends Alg
    This interface represents the algorithm that are able to be duplicated. Especially, the name of an algorithm that can be duplicated is retrieved by looking up the field "duplicated_alg_name" in its configuration. If such field does not exist, users define particular name via the returned value of getName() method.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
